WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.800
I built CleanCut for people who need to clean up a video before sharing it.

00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:09.200
Drop in a video or choose a folder from your Mac.

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:14.000
Choose mute profanity, subtitles, convert to MP4, or run them together.

00:00:14.000 --> 00:00:19.200
CleanCut processes the video privately on your Mac. It does not upload the file anywhere.

00:00:19.200 --> 00:00:23.800
Open the clean copy, subtitle file, or converted MP4 beside the original.

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:28.600
Public beta is open now. Try 3 videos free, with a lifetime launch deal for $19.99.
